entries.journal_entry_description: Draykken Bender sent to find and help his brother, Louis Bender, outside of Kor Vella.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the delivery depot outside of Kor Vella and meet with Louis Bender.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Louis Bender was taken by Bossk, a notorious bounty hunter. You to meet with Bossk and find a way to fre Louis Bender.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Bossk has forced you to fight the Bofa Treat Gang so that he can collect the bounty on them. He is holding Louis Bender as collateral in case you fail.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Bossk and let him know that the Bofa Treat Gang is no more.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Defeat Lucien, the leader of the Bofa Treat Gang.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Defeat Bofa Treat thugs in their hideout.
